pyarduino
------------------------------
Play with arduino using python

pyarduino is a python library for RAAP (Remote Arduino Automation Protocol) client, to remotely communicate and perform I/O among other things, with arduino board using Serial connection.

The "RAAP" firmware used with current release is available in "firmware" directory, Latest firmware can be downloaded, compiled & flashed from "RAAP" Github repository.
  
HOW TO
-------------
 Follow test_pyarduino.py  